ound"]]}," (the deepest fiord in NZ)"]},"\n",{"type":"*","value":[" Explore ",{"type":"[[","value":[["The Catlins"]]}," and walk through the native forest and along the coast. Look out for the fur seals, Hector's dolphins and yellow-eyed penguins."]},"\n",{"type":"==","value":["Eat"]}," \n\n",{"type":"==","value":["Drink"]}," \n\n",{"type":"==","value":["Sleep"]},"\nBackpacker Hostels are a cheap alternative to motels. Most offer double, single, twin or shared rooms.\n\n",{"type":"==","value":["Go next"]}," \n\n",{"type":"{{","value":[["outlineregion"]]},"\n",{"type":"{{","value":[["IsPartOf"],["South Island"]]},"\n",{"type":"{{","value":[["related"],["Driving_in_New_Zealand"]]},"\n\n",{"type":"[[","value":[["WikiPedia:Southland (region), New Zealand"]]},"\n",{"type":"[[","value":[["Dmoz:Regional\/Oceania\/New Zealand\/Southland"]]}]